# AI Rules Router

This project uses modular AI instructions located in the .skills/ directory. 
Always refer to the relevant skill folder before performing tasks:

- **Core Dart & Style**: See @.skills/effective-dart/SKILL.md
- **Flutter Architecture**: See @.skills/flutter-app-architecture/SKILL.md
- **State Management**: 
    - Provider: @.skills/provider/SKILL.md
    - BLoC: @.skills/bloc/SKILL.md
    - Riverpod: @.skills/riverpod/SKILL.md
- **Firebase**: See @.skills/firebase-*/SKILL.md
- **Testing**: See @.skills/testing/SKILL.md

When working on a specific feature, read the relevant skill first to ensure compliance with the documented best practices.
